Gosh.

It's been about 2-3 years since i last rock climbed. Went to Climb Asia with Sis and Rudy today after school. had to go recap on climbing stuff. I still, till now cant do a figure of 8 properly XD keep having trouble knotting safety line. Belaying's waaaaaaay easier.

Was doing my first route when my sister suddenly told me she wanted to tell me something. and i was like hmm maybe my butt looks ugly or something up hanging in the air. turns out that all she wanted to tell me that, that black clothed dude that just came in was Taufik... I was like er. okay.. intresting. Anyway, i didnt climb much. or rather i didnt finish many routes. lol. out of the dunno how many i tried only managed to complete two XD hand/arms damn tired. even till now i cant grip something properly. seems to take alot of strenght, which i dont have at the moment. after when Rudy and i got so shagged. Went into boulder area to watch my sister and her friends. apparently she hurt her shoulder and ankle.. again...

Sigh. Just the second night that he's gone. they're having some crap conversation. Which i dont want to be involved in. and seriously hope they DONT THINK about getting me involved. I kinna cant be bothered anymore.

Tired.. Still have community fiesta event tomorrow sat. sure gonna be an intresting two days.

It's been ten long years since Harry Potter has been released. and the final book is out. what a long wait. been reading the book since i got home from Fun on Foot today. quite tired atm. I must say that it was something i really never expected. but quite satisfied with the ending. :)

still remember that outta my entire series. I didnt actually buy all my books at all. I got my first three free in a boxed set fro Chai Hoon Jiejie for christmas one year. and at that time i was still in primary school. wondering - but not bothering to find out, why everyone was so crazy over Harry Potter. it wasnt till one day i really got so freaking bored i decided to open the first book. if i wasnt wrong i actually found the first book to be draggy. Might be due to the fact that i actually wasnt really intrested in the book. but was just something i was reading just to pass my time due to boredom. was only after that - than i got hooked on it. So i give my thanks. to the one who introduced me to the world of Harry Potter :D

okay. i better go. apparently more tired than i think i am.. gonna sleep. urgh. now that i've gotten HP7 outta the way. its time i get my c.maths back into pespective. first test next wed. Yikes better make a note somewhere. and sheesh did i mention my power supply unit died on me? Gah!

There are not many people i'd do stupid things for. :/ but you're one of em.

PEARLENE KEY KHEE


HAPPY 8TEEN GIRL!

6 years since i've met you. it's surprising how time flies. Was just in sec one that you/me asked to sit beside you/me? (i dont remember :X) and now. here we are. after secondary school. walking our own paths doing what we have to do. And what you need to do is to remember your goal and dont give up! I believe in what you can do, even with all the troubles that life throws at you., it'll make you a better person :) Happy Birthday once again girl. <3

ps: when you turn 21 it'll be 9 years XD

it's been ages since i'ved stayed at chalets. last time i think i did was in primary school. during those days every year my parents would have booked chalet for at least once a year. I do remember that the last time it was only me and jie though. Parents werent with us. i think i remember getting spooked about something. and i did go for a midnight cycling around. i think there were kitten's too. hmm..

anyway. went to Pk's chalet yesterday. Met up with bunch of em. Benson, June, Wanting, Si Xiu, Teck Kiat, Terence, Jun Hong, Agnus Agnes >.<, and duh.. Lene of cuz. So many people. than me June and Benson found corners to hide in. Heh. Had fun talkin to em. fooling around together once again just for a day. Watched my first F1 race. Drank my first non-dialuted er alcohol - not that i actually drink. (glad that i didnt get drunk - since i drank it by accident >.>) psst. Pk's such a weird sleeper :X imagine 4 of us accomadating to her just cuz she was sleeping in some funny place. Haha. Five girls sharing two single beds. another 3 people on the floor. and i think 6 people tonning outside yaking away. fell asleep towards the ending of F1. got woken up again after it was finished. since Wt and Daph was trying to figure out how to squeeze in the bed. Which we just ended up sleeping with half our bodies dangling off the end. Damn cold. wonder who's idea it was to have the fan and aircon on at the same time. went for breakkie at mac. ah dang. havent eaten mac breakfast in soooooooooo long. damn full now too. took some photos. watched abit of tv. some lame cartoon and Ellennnn. She has a hunted nose XD finally decided to get my lazy ass outta there. haha! was so late by than lah. Left with Terence and Agnus. couldnt make up my mind if i was gonna go back for steamboat later. 

Urgh. You know what? thought i didnt stay up. (like how i said i most prob would) i'm still tired >.> maybe that's a mental thingy. hmm. i'd know what it is anyway if i do really fall asleep later :P but for now. got some lame presentation that i've to go through -_- meh.

&*(#^%(*#)(%*(*#&*(#^&*(^ my blardy post is gone due to an 500 page error when i was posting. dang. pffft.two weeks left to go. than i'm back to my normal/abnormal school hours. depending on how you see it. nothing much really has been happening during attachment. last week had awards presention. group was reunited for 2 days. back to our usual (uh if ladies bitch what do guys do? >.<) talking of crap. haha. was fun seeing them again. i shall not comment on the people who came asking us questions. anyway we still gotta think of something to get for her. hmm. now lets see.met up with Benson and Wt on friday :D was so last minute la! it was only friday itself messages were flying around to confirm stuff. went down to Suntec to walk around pc show. went to msq for dinn at Billy Bombers after that xD between Wt and i we ate an entire chicken lol. had fun talkin bout the past and now. those days when we went crazy in secondary school. ah.

was lucky i didnt buy everything i was eyeing. cuz parents went to pc show on sat. dad bought new router and wireless card xD pci one. and since he said that i could use it if i wanted. So. i wil.. Heh. anyway... i'm the only one using a desktop now. cuz his monitor burnt out or something ah. anyway just not working. which was why he bought a new laptop. acer one ah. than just replace with desktop outside. I'm wondering what's he gonna be doing with the old cpu *ehem* might go cop some parts if he isnt gonna use anymore >.< Heh. Like maybe try out his tv card. take his dvd drive. heehees. shh. see how things go. haha!

Oh right. gotta remember i've to email Wt. Meet Benson to pass him some stuff. and Oie Uncle! you're supposed to pass me your gb hor! Thanks :D
i dont know how long more i can take this. an entire day of peace. and suddenly banging of tables. breaking of glass. fuck.

Sometimes i hate him so much i fucking wish he was dead.


Do you feel like a man when you push her around?
Do you feel better now as she falls to the ground?
Well I'll tell you my friend, one day this world's going to end
as your lies crumble down, a new life she has found.

Face down in the dirt, she said,
this doesn't hurt, she said,
I finally had enough.

I wish it'll be soon.

i've always love my stash of vcd/videos. got a fair bit more to watch now :D just bought a couple. just watched one. Step Up was lovely. ahha. that gurl reminded me of natalya.

i'm 3 weeks closer to the holidays :D so glaaaaaaad. cant wait to go on break again. and than back to the crazy class hours. so much better than current hours i tell you. miss talkin to ma online mates. some totally no contact at all. least i still get to talk to a couple now. hope it doesnt thunder/lighting storm so much in the next couple of weeks. its freezing enough in the lab already. no need for additional help >.> waste the entire friday trying to figure out something which she didnt want. zxzxzxzxz all we actually had to do was put something we already had into the pda laaaaaaaaaah. so lamb. pfft. oh yea. friday. HAHA i met Jesus Christ!! lmao!! freaky lah. was going back from school with Sean and Ernie than there was this siao guy at T.merah mrt station going around randomly talkin to people. said hi. introduced himself as Jesus Christ and than said he came back from whereever blah blah blah. PIANG EH. ignored him and he went away lol. than after getting on the train. ernie and sean sat. and than there was this dude (i think from same school not sure though) playing songs on his phone loudly ah. somemore super old songs. whahahaha. 


i had really crap connection this afternoon :( was busy doing stuff somemore when i was thrown outta the internet. gah. got so pissed. but that got me to realised that we had wireless@sg now. hahahaha. xD should try it out soon. see how it is. 

btw sorry fizah >.< i posted that post but no idea what to reply LOL! Sowie!

Watching She's the man tomorrow. maybe happy feet too?  not sure. see how :D taking this time to catch up on my movies >.< shhh. only till we actually start on our project :X

was so tired yesterday :S after school went home and fell right into bed. only woke up this morning >.< gosh that was totally nuts i tell ya. more than 12 hours of sleep sia! reached home about six plus i think. Hmmm. so maybe i'll stay up later tonight? ahhaha! we'll see..

okay. time to find something to do now. till next time!

hmm never knew they had a song called hello friend. intresting. and i'm remember some old forgotten songs *ehem* that i dont have on my player

i'm gonna get their albums to keep. :) lucky i still got ang pow money to spent LOLOL!

Made sure Faisal woke up, used the com for a wee bit and went out to meet him. Wah. Think its the earliest time i ever headed into town man. Even before noon. Had to walk around ALOT before his Fred Perry stall opened. found out abit more about Far east. and the fact that it actually has a nail school and a fair bit of tatoo parlours. Heh. 

I FINALLY GOT MY STICKMAN xD

Havent felt true hunger in some time. Havent excatly had proper food these past two days. Just a couple of oreo sticks, ikan bilis and chips. Hence now hungry in the middle of the night.

Anyway, results release yesterday. Woke up in a fright. dreaming about bad results =/ and happened to talk on msn with one of my online friends and scared the crap outta her. lol. cuz she had her volume on high. ahha! Okay. wasnt that bad. I shall refrain from saying how i could do better. because i suppose i already did good judging from what i heard. here goes anyway. 

3.8 GPA !!!!!!!!

Wooooooo. no c/d's like i thought i would get. >.< apparently my sister didnt do as good. *clears her throat* than again i'm in school much more than her.

Enough about results. its the holidays ;) got about two more weeks before i gotta head for orientation and IA shit. Been spending alot of time online with a group of friends. and dang. had so much fun using ts just now xD thought i didnt talk much. Haha. maybe soon. Been having so much fun with em. Just sad that we're all spread out :( Min Pk Lanica, Di, Ea, Shy, Jack, Lin xD

Right... talking. just remember. Monday had to go back for b.leader. and suddenly in the middle of it i get a call asking me to go for some interview. i was like huhhhhhhh. Gosh i seriously hope i do NOT get it. :S though what Mindy says is true. looks good when applying for jobs and stuff. But damn. was telling her i dont wanna be such an Obvious! "role model". Sheesh. oh right gotta go back a couple of more days for b.leader too. next week i think. not gonna bother till then. Oh right! and wth!!! Ms Preethi's taking over SICT B.L LOLLOOOOOOL! Seriously =/ Shall see how things go xD as to what i know first few days of orientation i think she's busy. Was mentioning about how we're supposed to report to patrick instead for schoo IA cuz she having master's exams???

ps: finally shopping for my bag xD Hopefully i'll get my lazy arse out soon to get it. ahha! still trying to decide which to buy though. Heh.

Rosel. Auntie! we need to meet up one day. tell me what happened about KI dinner perhaps soon? =D

and uhhh. help me wish Fred Happy Belated Birthday >.< Heh.

Correction, not sleepy to get to sleep. seriously bad of me. but i have to say i havent touched my book at all for my paper on monday. quite a listless mood. dont feel like doing any studying at all though my brain have told myself umpteen times i gotta pick it up and read. 

went to IT fair on thurs/friday. scouted but didnt really get what i wanted. shall drag my lazy arse to sim lim one day i suppose.  stinky IT fairs mostly selling external hdds. dang. memory card prices are damn low. gosh. i had to keep myself from buying one just for the low price lol. i already have so many lying around! i have like two 256mb's (sd) , two 512mb (mmc) and like one 1gig (sd). i still have my eye on that bag. havent really spent my cny money. haha. sis did thought. she bought a HUGE timbuk2 bag which i hijacked. its currently lying in my room on the floor! if she aint gonna take it back its gonna be mine xD heh.

ahh. well i suppose i should put time to good use. and try bash infomation into my head regarding the blah blah blah seven osi layers. blah blah blah tcpip model. blah blah blah routing protocals. blah blah blah acls (ithink) blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah exam sucks blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah exams really suck big time blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah blah  theory's a bore blah blah blah blah blah blah

sem's coming to an end. the "last (unoffical)" day of school tml (by right is friday. but friday class all cancelled). phase test is finally over. was ok overall. both for networkin and wad. wasnt much of a problem i guess. but for wad felt that the timing was a tad bit too short. dragged like almost another 45-60. have to say sorry to patrick and abang's class lol cuz they were supposed to use the lab after that. two major things left with school now is just wad project (final submission) and of cuz that dreaded networking exam. urgh. i gotta start picking up my book mannnn.

big day's coming up. but thing's arent really good i suppose. firstly head's been a bitch today. on off on off pain. throat hurts too. too much new year goodies i think? maybe with the additional talkin i've been doing for practice. was telling sean today that now when cough phlegm out now got blood. no idea why though :S sighh.

had a nice after talk with the guys today after dinner. just cuz waiting for time to become 8. know why? just so that sean and andrew can cab back without paying surcharge! -_- lol. anyway, there's so many things going on in our small lil world. hahahahaha!! quite surprisingly some stuff that i heard. had a nice lil laugh over some matters too. xD but i'm sure i'm bound to miss em in the year to come. sigh. changes.

had a nice little haul this year for CNY! my much loved bank account is getting fatter and fatter!! yay! which is good. haha. treated mua mamma nice lil jap meal that day. :) have i ever mentioned i love her to bits? heh. though she likes to drag me all over central clothes shopping lol.

oh ya. sister just came back from malaysia. she bought me that weird lil mint/icing donut again. *frowns* urgh. ohhhhhhhhh my fridggie is stuff with iceeeeeeecream xD shhhh. not telling ya what. later you come steal. whooooooooooops!

okieeeeeeeeeeeeeeeees i gotta go rest that silly thing called my head. ciao!

i got so fustrated during test today =( just gave up man. damn asp.net test. sheeeeeeeeeeeesh. still wondering if its a human error or pc. stupid page keeps show repeated entries though its okay on database. bah! i guess i have to be thankful for the fact i didnt fail -_- geez. have to just do better for phase test next week lor. seriously hope no stupid errors like today again. sigh.

on the other hand......... internal selections were TOOOOOOOOOODAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAY! and we got thru =D the only ICT team from CE hoho. and we got five outta five votes from internal judges =] ms p says whatever we do. we must have confidence in what we're doing. and weiguang's nick says we MUST WIN the competition. ahaha. shhhh. ah well at least internal's are over. get to get abit of a break before we chiong for finals :) hope dont have to go home so late this week. might be nice to actually come home when the sun's up for once lol.

anyway quite tired. stayed up the whole night to go school early. cuz i'm in the super bad habit of offing my snooze like ten times and finally getting my lazy arse outta bed to totally shut my alarm and than go back to sleep heh. oops. =X

geez. how can a long week seem to pass so fast? spent everyday after school preparing for presentation. urgh, ate so much junk lol. never a day passed without us munching on something. be it nerds or pringles. lol for a moment thought was gonna get a sore throat. ahha. no lost of voice though :X had a false alarm on friday. suposed to have internal selections. but some bigshot couldnt make it so was postponed to monday. sigh. yet another day of waking up early.

school's been okay. finally made our year two selection. still have time to change our minds until coming friday. lol. decided to pick networking in the end. aha but if you ask me for a reason i wouldnt be able to tell ya one. heh. anyway if i seriously suck that badly at networking i'll be pushed to multimedia in the end. -_- but really trying to maintain my current grade. sigh. but in my mind currently i think i cant make it lah. not only for nwt but for cms also lol. could be due to the *ehem* teachers and my intrest in it lor. glad that the postponed presentation allows me to *ehem* skip abit (hopefully more) of my cms lesson heh. if only i can do that for like another uhm three more weeks? than i think the term is up *yay* =X prob get nagged at if someone sees this lol.

hmmm. moment of unrest might be soon be calm. it all depends on what happens when He returns. a moment's pain a moment's heartache the guilt the lies. its time for the beginning.

life's been pretty much a game to me nowadays. just waiting for moves and seeing what happens. how he and she proceeds. mel says my motto in life now is why bother. haha. and i shall not comment ;] life's been oooooookay nowadays. if things happen they happen if it doesnt it doesnt. just passing each day one at a time. same thing happens each day. school home school home. nothing much in my life. making abit more effort to be there for her. thats all. so that she can go on each day. just as i do. just that it's harder for her. sigh. how i wish i could spare her from all this pain. grrr.

Sagittarius Personality
Bold, dashing and spirited. It's a bit difficult to keep pace with you - whether it is in your movements or in your speech. You like to be free as the wind that blows, quite uncaring of the effect you may have on your surroundings. You could not care less and hate being in an atmosphere that is physically or emotionally claustrophobic. Somewhat lacking in tact, your foot-in-the-mouth syndrome could do with a little thought. Nevertheless, you are honest but more than a little tactless. Sagittarians are ambitious - always aiming higher than the goal they initially set for themselves. You love challenges and are too full of energy to sit still. Although you see yourself more as a sportsperson than an intellectual, you secretly enjoy reading, writing, and exploring subjects unknown to you. You are a good learner and would do extremely well as an academician. You are quite popular, albeit a bit unconventional and are loyal to your friends. Many of you enjoy the patronage of influential people but unfortunately; you will also have your share of enemies who mean serious harm. You are often driven by excitement and can be a bit ungainly when in this state; sweeping gestures tend to send things flying. You are sometimes insecure and edgy. You tend to doubt your decisions and judgement. The advice is - trust your instinct. Avoid going by what people tell you if you want to succeed in your work. A word of caution though -- your instincts may not work too well when you are betting, gambling and speculating, and you may end up losing heavily.

Sagittarius Lover
Although affectionate and loving, Sagittarians are not apt to be too demonstrative. Not much cuddling, showering of gifts, or saying it with roses - something that may be misconstrued as lack of warmth. However, you will make it exciting enough for your beloved. Bungee jumping, mountain climbing, horse riding, going to exotic destinations... all this you will do with your partner. Besides fellow Sagittarians, you will find ideal life partners in Aries and Leo, being closer to your temperament than any other zodiac sign, only they will be able to share your excitement. Marriage with someone who is not able to keep up with your pace may be a failure, so make sure the person cuddling up tight in your roller coaster life is screaming in fun and not fear. You are a loving and playful person and though you are not prepared for children, you make a good parent; you use your enormous patience while dealing with them, giving them the respect they deserve. You are a risk-taker and are often attracted to danger. You should exercise caution as your family depends on you. Sagittarian homes have a distinct mark of their personality. Simply lifting ideas from elsewhere will not do for them -- they like to be a little different.

Sagittarius Professional
You will do well in most occupations that require you to be outdoors. You make good sporting people. You will also succeed as teachers, lawyers, and politicians. Business and banking too are good for you. If you find your work tedious, it is simply a signal for you change to something more exciting. Jupiter, the symbol of good fortune, riches, and status, rules you. Although you will achieve most of this, it will be rather late in life. In fact, up to the age of 30, you are likely to suffer financial setbacks, mostly because of your tendency to be rash. However, you learn well from your mistakes and these monetary setbacks are not going to upset you too much. In fact, even when you are well settled financially, you will not particularly crave for landed property and assets.

Sagittarius Traveller
You dislike going for a peaceful quiet holiday away from the hustle-bustle. The idea is to have fun and frolic on holidays rather than lying with a book. You are born travelers so if possible would visit all the places given in a tourist book. You are open to having a trekking and camping holiday.

Sagittarius Teens
This is a young woman you can always count on, and most of the times, she is fun to be with. The Sagittarius girl never lacks company; she is bubbling with energy and ready to explore any thing. She certainly has the gift of the gab but her tendency to blurt out whatever's on her mind can land her in a mess. People around won't understand that she is simply being honest. If she finds something interesting she will simply go for it. She is not the kind to spend long hours in front of the mirror and happily shares her wardrobe with other girls. The young Sagittarius will excel at school and is likely to travel to another country for higher studies.

A Sagittarian young man is steeped in the spirit of adventure and loves to roam the world more than anything else. He dreams on a grand scale. And what is interesting -- this has a good chance of coming true! He has a fiercely independent spirit and finds it really hard to commit himself to anything. The best thing about him is that he is open to all kinds of ideas and this wins him a lot of friends, and lovers as well. Another reason for his popularity is his carefree, fun loving nature, and the enormous generosity that he bestows on his friends. He has a lot of energy bottled up and sports provide just one outlet. The Sagittarian will spend his life chasing wild dreams


Sagittarius Kids
A happy-go-lucky kid, the Sagittarius child needs to travel all over the place and enjoy his or her freedom to the fullest. Characterised by a positive attitude to life and high energy levels, this kid gets naturally attracted to sports and has an open mind and easily mingles with a diverse group of friends, mindful of being fair and just to all of them. The Sagittarius kid is very talkative but his or her brand of candour can often spell trouble, which is of course cheerfully overlooked by most people.

Sagittarius Well Being
Sagittarians are fun loving, carefree individuals who live life to the fullest. As a result, they generally do not suffer from stress-related problems. However, most Sagittarians tend to take everything very casually, including their health. They rarely, if ever, visit a doctor, because they seldom require to. Sagittarians are the most daring and audacious of all the signs of the zodiac. They are always ready to try-out a new sport or adventure. The only problem is that Sagittarians are prone to minor strains, sprains and injuries. You will have to learn to take it easy and learn to do warm up's etc before putting your body through heavy exercises. Also, give yourself enough time to heal before embarking on any new escapades. A good diet of fresh fruit and vegetables, meat and dairy products should keep you on an even keel, with the occasional time out to rest and relax. A good complexion, shining eyes and a prominent nose are your distinctive features. Some of you may, however, suffer from nervous disorders. Sagittarius rules the motor functions and the lower limbs that in some cases may be vulnerable to injury.

Sagittarius Luck
Autumn colours like yellow, bright orange and rust browns, turquoise and a splash of purple are colours that will bring you good luck. Your lucky stones is turquoise. You are lucky with number 3. Jupiter is your ruler and your element is fire.
